nodes.text: During the Galactic Civil War, a high-ranking Alliance to Restore the Republic officer was under the protection of Shroud Team in Corint City on the planet Pirik. Thilis-Brin, an Ishi Tib member of the team, ensured the officer's safety by evading Imperial scout troopers in a high-speed speeder bike pursuit through the Talamp Industrial Sector. Thilis-Brin successfully delivered the officer to the required destination while avoiding being identified.
